  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the postoperative pain after general anesthesia of
      orbital diseases and ocular tumor patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate patients diagnosed of orbital diseases or ocular
      tumor over 16 years old of the postoperative pain after general anesthesia , and to analyze
      the related factors of pain after operation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
